# 📮 AI No-Code Email Security Automation System  
### Built with AppSheet • Make.com • Gmail API • Google Sheets • AI  

---

# 🚀 Project Overview  
This system automatically:  
✔ Filters and categorizes Gmail messages  
✔ Identifies promotions, newsletters, spam-like patterns  
✔ Sends cleaned data to Google Sheets  
✔ Displays insights in an AppSheet front-end  
✔ Runs secure automation workflows in Make.com  
✔ Applies AI classification to summarize email intent  

Designed as part of my **Co.Lab No-Code AI Apprenticeship**.

---

# 🧩 System Architecture  
![System Architecture](./system-diagram.png)

**Workflow Summary:**  
1. Gmail → Make.com (Email watch module)  
2. Make.com → Google Sheets (data storage)  
3. AppSheet → UI for users  
4. Optional: OpenAI → classification & email summary  

---

# 🛠️ Tech Stack  
- AppSheet (Front-end application)  
- Make.com (Automation workflows)  
- Gmail API (Email ingestion)  
- Google Sheets (Backend database)  
- OpenAI (AI classification – optional)

